North opens 1\S - what do you respond? [bid 2D]
You responds 2\D, natural and game forcing.  North rebids 2\s.  In our style of 2/1, this promises 6+ cards in spades, and denies a side 4-card suit.  What should we bid now? [bid 4s]
[show NS]
You should jump to 4\S. This is Fast Arrival, indicating a minimum hand with no particular interest in slam.
North is happy to rest in the game contract.
